message.body: Howdy! Were you thinking of stopping by today to grab the tape? Or did I miss you? No sweat, no rush either way. It's ready anytime (I'll just be out tomorrow)
Hey! I'm just getting here! In the lobby!
Sorry to have missed you! It looks INCREDIBLE. So thrilled.
So sorry I missed you - got pulled into a call. Thank you, and have a wonderful next couple of weeks!
